items.description:
High Quality Dreambooth (JP's 24gb repo) trained LoRA of the character Hans Gruber from the movie "Die Hard" (portrayed by Alan Rickman) . Created using only hi-definition stills of Hans from the film and nothing else. Trained with Dreambooth and then the LoRA was extracted using the A1111 extension "Supermerger"

Trigger with "Hansgruber person"

(yes, put person also). Use "Hi-Res fix" for best results. Use prompt weighting and/or Controlnet to get maximum flexibility out of this likeness model.

Note on the Samples:

The 16x9 movie style wide images were generated with help of Control Net. I don't think Civitai notes if Controlnet was used but you may not be able to reproduce some of the images due to that. (I often use canny w/ a random movie still for a % of the early steps to guide the image to do something interesting).

Note on the model:

Use the original Stable Diffusion models (v1.4, v1.5, etc) for best likeness results.

「崩壊：スターレイル」のキャラクターモデルをすべて作るのは体力の関係上難しいのですが、欲しいキャラクターがあればコメントにメッセージを残していただければ作成させていただきます。

items.name: Zeitgeist - Semi-Realistic Concept Digital Art (Style LoRa for SDXL)
items.description:
See here for an extensive article about my entire training workflow and configuration if you want to train your own SDXL 1.0 LoRa's and achieve results similar as me!

Recommended weight: 1.0 - or lower when you combine it with other LoRa's

Recommended model and VAE: SDXL 1.0 with 0.9 vae

Recommended settings: 35 steps | DPM++ 2M Karras | CFG 7

Recommended negative prompt: text, watermark, signature, abstract, burned, instagram, low-quality, low-res, action figure, child drawing, jpeg, low contrast, glossy, puppet, cliché, stock photo, magazine cover

Description

A semi-realistic concept digital art artstyle LoRa for SDXL 1.0, aimed at delivering high-quality digital art in the style of concept artworks, like which you could find on Artstation.

Trigger words

  • "artwork in xvst artstyle"

Changelog

v3.0

  • much increased artstyle likeness

v2.0

  • name change from "Realistic Digital Art" to "Semi-Realistic Concept Digital Art"

  • retrained using a lower learning rate, overtraining has been basically completely eliminated - diversity and flexibility has been massively increased

v1.0

  • Initial release

Additional Info

Credit is not mandatory but I would still appreciate credit when posting images using these LoRa's on social media! Feel free to @ my Twitter and/or Instagram accounts too (@ai_characters)! I would love to know when it is used!

I share all of my model's and training knowledge for free, but donations to my Ko-Fi would be greatly appreciated! Testing so much and training so many model's costs a lot of money (and time).

Feel free to also try out my RVC2 AI voice models which you can find here!

Stats (v3.0)

Dataset:

  • 49 artworks

Epoch chosen for the final models:

  • 25

Learning rate:

  • 3e-5

For the configuration used to train this model see my guide which I linked in the beginning of this post.

items.name: BallpointPainting
items.description:
Introducing the inaugural style Toolkit from the AWPainting Toolkit series for AIGC: The BallpointPainting Style Toolkit.

Usage Guidelines:

This toolkit is adept at emulating the aesthetics of ballpoint or gel pen drawings, integrating certain characteristics reminiscent of etchings. It's highly compatible with 2D graphics and even realistic models.

LoRA Weight Setting: 0.7-1

Preferred Model: AWPainting1.1

Trigger Keywords: ballpoint pen drawing.

Leveraging this specific trigger is pivotal to produce pure black or blue strokes. In the absence of this trigger, the output will default to a colored sketch style.

AWPainting Toolkit 系列的第一款画风Toolkit——圆珠笔画风BallpointPainting

使用说明：

此画风Toolkit可以比较好的复现出圆珠笔或中性笔绘的风格，也有一定的类似版画的效果，搭配2D甚至真人模型都可以有不错的效果，更多玩法请各位自行发掘。

权重推荐：0.7-1

大模型推荐：AWPainting1.1

触发词：ballpoint pen drawing，一定要使用触发词才能有纯黑或纯蓝色的线条，如果不使用触发词，就会变成有填色的勾线风格。

items.name: majogari mix
items.description:
・NAIを含まないイラストモデル。
・主にtrainDifference機能で、学習モデルと学習モデル同士のマージモデルのみを使用。
・個性的な色彩、人気モデルとは異なったキャラクターデザインなど。
・混ぜたモデルの傾向から、おそらくはファンタジーも得意なはずだが、よく分からない。
・前髪に偏りがあるので、そこを変更するプロンプトを知っていれば役に立つかも。
（swept bangs、blunt bangsなど）
・Danbooruタグは利用可能だが、やや癖があり。弱いと感じたら強度を上げると効くはず。
・プロンプトによっては、背景が強すぎる傾向があり、背景の強度を下げると人物の比重が増す。
・NSFWも出せるが、どの程度優れているかは分からない。
・作例は少女、城、水彩少女、ドラゴン。

・Illustration model without NAI.
・Only training models and merged models between training models were used, mainly in the trainDifference function.
・Unique colors, character designs that differ from popular models, etc.
・The tendency of the mixed models suggests that perhaps fantasy is also a strong suit, but I'm not sure.
・Because the bangs in the image are biased, it might be useful if you knew the prompt to change it.
(swept bangs, blunt bangs, etc.)
・Danbooru tags can be used, but there are some peculiarities. If you feel weak, increase the intensity and it should work.
・Some prompts tend to have too strong a background, and reducing the background strength increases the weight of the person.
・Examples are a girl, a castle, a watercolor girl, and a dragon.
・This can also generate NSFW, but I don't know how good it is.

Add/remove bandages or thigh highs: asymettrical legwear / bare legs / bandaged arm

Add/remove panties: black panties / no panties

Add belt: belt

Add staff (a bit buggy, needs some work): staff

Remove bra: no bra

How to use LoRA in A1111:

  • Copy the .safetensors file to stable-diffusion-webui/models/lora

  • Add <lora:megumin_v1:1> to your prompt (or use a plugin)

April Bowlby (b. 1980) is an American actress and model. Fans of unkillable CBS sitcoms will know her as Jon Cryer's wife (briefly) in "Two and a Half Men" and Barney Stinson's ex in "How I Met Your Mother." Lifetime watchers will remember her from "Drop Dead Diva." Those who spend time in the DC Cinematic Universe may know her as Rita Farr, a.k.a. Elasti-Girl, in "Titans" and the recently concluded "Doom Patrol."

This embedding is based on 30 images, cooked for a total of 300 steps on base SD1.5: 16 vectors per token, a 0.004 learning rate, a batch size of 6, and 5 gradient steps.

Your ratings, especially of the five-star variety, are very much appreciated.

items.name: Game of Thrones
items.description:
❤️ Support this model ... 🫶 Discord Server ... How was it made?
👀 See also: 🌶️ Sassy Girls 👑 Game of Thrones ❤️‍🔥 Divas ❄️ Frozen Animation 💖 Babes 2.0 🍑 Babes 1.1 🍒 Sexy Toons feat. Pipa 💋 Babes Kissable Lips 👩🏽‍🎤 Noa Kirel.
ℹ️ This model was trained on the first three episodes of the TV show Game of Thrones. 9k images focused on characters' faces (50 subjects in total), and 4k images from different scenes. Additionally, 30k images were used as regularization images - medieval-themed images and half of the ❤️‍🔥 Divas dataset.
ℹ️ Trigger word for style is "game of thrones" - using it negative prompt can help to make brighter images. Characters' names that can be used as trigger words:

ned stark, jon snow, catelyn stark, daenerys targaryen, robert baratheon, arya stark, joffrey baratheon, tyrion lannister, jaime lannister, robb stark, petyr baelish, littlefinger, sansa stark, bran stark, cersei lannister, viserys targaryen, jorah mormont, benjen stark, waymar royce, rakharo dothraki, will ranger, jeor mormont, doreah handmaid, irri dothraki, maester luwin, khal drogo, the hound, sandor clegane, lord varys, rast ranger, rodrik cassel, maester aemon, mycah butcher son, grenn ranger, gared ranger, theon greyjoy, ser barristan selmy, jory cassel, ros cook, yoren recruiter, wildling girl, royal steward, catspaw assassin, pypar steward, old nan, illyrio mopatis, ilyn payne, lancel lannister, renly baratheon, mikken blacksmith, alliser thorne, syrio forel

ℹ️ This model is based on ❤️‍🔥 Divas model - original training, remixed recipe, and half of the dataset used for regularization.
ℹ️ My goal was to achieve high accuracy of characters, which was challenging due to the limited amount of frames/angles/lighting/scenes of many characters. I had to pull a few tricks out of my sleeves, but I think that most of the characters look very accurate.
